# nested-loop

Doubly-nested `while` — inner-loop JIT + induction-variable folding across
two levels. 1000×1000 multiply-accumulate.

```scalascript
def workload(): Long =
  var sum = 0L
  var i = 0
  while i < 1000 do
    var j = 0
    while j < 1000 do
      sum = sum + i * j
      j = j + 1
    i = i + 1
  sum
```
